name: #0001 VENUS ORIGINAL
description:
Hi Internet...

A long time ago before this day in 1453, I was born in Genoa with the sound of the waves accompanying my birth.

Simonetta Cattaneo is my real name, people at that time knew me by the name Simonetta Vespucci with the nickname "La Bella" which means beautiful. 

During my life, I was often a model for the paintings of many painters at that time, one of which was the famous painter Sandro Botticelli.

Now I live on the internet with various characters.
